<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>永旺</title><link>https://aeon.co/feed.atom</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:15:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与相对主义的斗争</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/86d431d8-d3cd-4891-8f6b-aabd112c5c66/header_essay-goya-6985.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;伯纳德·威廉姆斯认为，一个人的道德是由文化和历史塑造的。但这并不意味着每个人都是对的&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——丹尼尔·卡尔卡特&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>房间</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/against-her-fathers-warnings-debra-resolves-to-learn-about-his-time-in-auschwitz?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/335f55d2-5a3c-4c26-b174-edbbe6a9fca7/header_the-room-landscape-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;濒临死亡的父亲向女儿讲述了他在奥斯威辛集中营的经历。他的故事成为她无法离开的房间&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/against-her-fathers-warnings-debra-resolves-to-learn-about-his-time-in-auschwitz?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/against-her-fathers-warnings-debra-resolves-to-learn-about-his-time-in-auschwitz?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>一场破坏社会的考试</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/why-chinese-minds-still-bear-the-long-shadow-of-keju?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="许多身着传统服饰的人物聚集在一个悬挂着纸质清单的结构下方。前景是马。颜色随着年龄的增长而变得柔和" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/4e582db8-120d-48e8-bcfb-f718d171bc95/header_essay-ming-beamtenprufungen1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;科举是中国极其困难的公务员考试，它以自由和创造力为代价强化了国家力量&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——黄亚生&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-chinese-minds-still-bear-the-long-shadow-of-keju?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/why-chinese-minds-still-bear-the-long-shadow-of-keju?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>小丑简史</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-jesters-whove-spoken-truth-to-power-around-the-globe-and-across-centuries?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/79eaf5a4-9760-446f-8277-279c6541b304/header_a-brief-history-of-jesters-landscape-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;从逃跑的箭到释放囚犯，这部动画记录了小丑的愚蠢、重要、偶尔危险的工作&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-jesters-whove-spoken-truth-to-power-around-the-globe-and-across-centuries?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-jesters-whove-spoken-truth-to-power-around-the-globe-and-across-centuries?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>有生源论</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/panspermia-theory-dives-under-other-worlds-ocean-ice-crust?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/cb3c9018-281a-4497-be0d-2c1ad426b49d/header_essay-final-enceladus-11-30-10-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;有地下海洋的冰冻世界可能是有机生命的孵化器。但生命是怎么来的呢？&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——巴拉兹·布拉达克&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/panspermia-theory-dives-under-other-worlds-ocean-ice-crust?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/panspermia-theory-dives-under-other-worlds-ocean-ice-crust?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>从鱼到月亮</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/moments-of-poetry-pierce-through-the-mundane-at-a-small-town-grocery?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/f47e81da-97fe-40e2-a3e5-775d06a7a0a3/header_from-fish-to-moon-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;如何在微小的时刻和最不可能的地方找到诗歌——例如佛罗里达州帕霍基的一个小镇杂货店的故事&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/moments-of-poetry-pierce-through-the-mundane-at-a-small-town-grocery?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/moments-of-poetry-pierce-through-the-mundane-at-a-small-town-grocery?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>穿着鞋子祈祷</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/a-history-of-the-modern-islamic-movement-that-is-salafism?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/f532d693-423c-4e2a-b588-928d99f86696/header_essay-final-nyc125576.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;萨拉菲主义逊尼派运动诞生于20世纪初，目标是塑造七日生活&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——亚伦·洛克-辛格&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/a-history-of-the-modern-islamic-movement-that-is-salafism?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/a-history-of-the-modern-islamic-movement-that-is-salafism?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>人不是专业人士</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/how-peer-support-can-help-with-the-mental-health-care-crisis?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="一名妇女在鲜花丛中的空地上搀扶另一名妇女站起来。" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/16d84bad-9508-4c45-88d4-27b57d87cb47/header_this-final-ivyy-chen_04_aeon_v006.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;培训个人在困难时期互相支持是我们在心理健康危机中向前迈出的深刻一步&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——阿琼·卡普尔和茉莉花·卡哈&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/how-peer-support-can-help-with-the-mental-health-care-crisis?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/how-peer-support-can-help-with-the-mental-health-care-crisis?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>下Gd</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/how-jewish-leaders-in-the-us-are-fighting-abortion-bans-on-religious-grounds?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/4f56b99c-f69a-4608-91cc-109ef80cb6e2/header_under-g-d-landscape-4-v2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; “你是否利用宗教自由来保护原教旨主义基督徒？”反对美国堕胎禁令的犹太领导人&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/how-jewish-leaders-in-the-us-are-fighting-abortion-bans-on-religious-grounds?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/how-jewish-leaders-in-the-us-are-fighting-abortion-bans-on-religious-grounds?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>伟大的、被遗忘的沃尔夫</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/why-we-should-recover-the-philosophy-of-christian-wolff?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="一本 18 世纪德语书籍的扉页和卷首插图。书名是用红色哥特字体写的" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/2aa83030-88fd-4ccc-b4c9-a506700700fe/header_test.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;克里斯蒂安·沃尔夫的数学方法为外行人撰写，为女性和国王阅读，他的数学方法使他成为启蒙运动的关键哲学家&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——迈克尔·沃尔肖茨&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-we-should-recover-the-philosophy-of-christian-wolff?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/why-we-should-recover-the-philosophy-of-christian-wolff?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item></channel></rss>